法規內容.條文內容:
The protecting measures may be suspended if the protected individuals meet any of the following conditions:
1. the purpose of protection has been achieved;
2. the protected individual has gained the ability of self-sustain;
3. the protected individual has been assisted to obtain employment or entered school;
4. the protected individual has seriously violate the regulations of the Association of Rehabilitative Protection and its branch associations;
5. the protected individual has request for suspending the protection measures;
6. the Association of Rehabilitative Protection and its branch associations has made the decision that there is no necessary for the protection measures.
